Technical Skills

My strenghts lies in the front-end development of web applications. I have the most experience in developing websites using React.js and Redux with JavaScript but most of my resent works I use Next.js with Typescript. My final project in my BSc studies was a mobile application where I used React Native.

I think it is important to track the impacts of changes so I'm familiar with user tracking using Google Analytics and Tag Manager, f.ex. creating A/B tests and front-end bug tracking using Bugsnag.

I have created some simple full-stack applications using Node.js and Express for the web server, however at my workplace Python is used for the backend. There my focus lies in the front-end but I have implemented several tasks every now and then besides experience from my studies.
